name: Immortal Face: Jack o' Lantern
description:
Stingy Jack tricked the devil once.“Turn into a coin, so I can pay for my last drink.“ The devil agreed and got entrapped in his pocket, next to a crucifix. For his freedom, the devil spared Jack 10 years of his own.
	
Stingy Jack tricked the devil twice."Pick me an apple and I’ll gladly follow you after." The devil climbed a tree and Jack carved a cross on the bark. For his freedom, the devil granted Jack an everlasting one.

Stingy Jack died and denied by hell and heaven. The devil gifted him an ember for his lantern, and now Jack roamed the earth forever.

tjhinoz, 2021
